Package: finance.yahoo.com
Title: Yahoo Finance Client for R
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Sean", "B", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "support@scrapeable.com")
Description: Self-contained Yahoo Finance client returning tidy tibbles.
    Covers OHLCV history (all intervals), batch quotes, financial statements,
    key statistics, options chains, analyst recommendations, institutional/insider
    holders, earnings, dividends, splits, and company profiles. No xts/zoo
    dependency. Cookie/crumb auth handled transparently.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
Depends: R (>= 4.1.0)
Imports: httr2, jsonlite, dplyr, tibble
NeedsCompilation: no
